dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents land use for Waupaca County, Wisconsin in 2004. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Waupaca_LandUse_2004.gdb. [This file folder contains the coverage for the County of Waupaca's land use plus all of New London and Marion. It was an update (2003-2005) from the county and their communities. East Central aided in the changes as a service to the county.]
uw_supplemental_s: This metadata was updated to reflect that the data is no longer restricted and has been opened for public use. For complete metadata documentation and most current online dataset download, please visit http://data-waupacacounty.opendata.arcgis.com/ [Data have been coded and modified to match ECWRPC Digital Map Data Standards. To obtain a copy, contact the Distributor listed under Distribution Information.]
